    <item>
      <title>SK 集团支持基金将韩国芯片公司引入中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/sk-group-backs-fund-to-bring-south-korean-chip-firms-to-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美国正加大对其盟友的压力，要求其遏制北京的科技野心，SK 集团仍将资金投入一只新基金，旨在帮助韩国芯片公司在中国开设工厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/sk-group-backs-fund-to-bring-south-korean-chip-firms-to-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 09:33:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技公司如何掩盖人工智能的真实碳足迹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/ai-tech-giants-hide-dirty-energy-with-outdated-carbon-accounting-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[引领人工智能竞赛的科技巨头们已经找到了一种方法来掩盖其日益增长的电力使用对气候的影响：非捆绑的可再生能源证书。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/ai-tech-giants-hide-dirty-energy-with-outdated-carbon-accounting-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 09:00:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
