    <item>
      <title>LVMH 旗下丝芙兰中国业务裁员约 10% 因困境加深</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/sephora-layoffs-lvmh-cuts-10-of-staff-in-china-as-it-struggles-to-expand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，化妆品零售商丝芙兰正在中国裁员数百人。作为路威酩轩集团（LVMH）最大的品牌之一，丝芙兰正试图扭转在全球第二大经济体中国的亏损局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/sephora-layoffs-lvmh-cuts-10-of-staff-in-china-as-it-struggles-to-expand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 08:37:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国机构将参与对非洲纤维公司的2.25亿美元投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/us-agency-to-join-225-million-investment-in-african-fiber-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲光纤公司 Liquid Telecommunication Holdings Ltd. 首席执行官哈迪·佩姆希瓦 (Hardy Pemhiwa) 表示，一家美国开发机构将成为主要投资者之一，该公司计划在年底前筹集 2.25 亿美元的股权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/us-agency-to-join-225-million-investment-in-african-fiber-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 08:00:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿布扎比穆巴达拉通过收购 Yondr 加大数据中心投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/abu-dhabi-s-mubadala-adds-to-data-center-bets-with-yondr-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆巴达拉投资公司 (Mubadala Investment Co.) 正在投资总部位于伦敦的数据中心开发商 Yondr Group，这是阿布扎比财富基金进军该领域的最新举措，该领域预计将受益于对云服务和人工智能技术的旺盛需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/abu-dhabi-s-mubadala-adds-to-data-center-bets-with-yondr-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 07:43:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SoftwareOne 称出售谈判充满挑战，但取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/softwareone-talks-on-possible-sale-challenging-but-progressing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SoftwareOne Holding AG 表示，由于其盈利未达预期且下调了全年收入预期，该公司正在与多家公司就潜在出售事宜进行谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/softwareone-talks-on-possible-sale-challenging-but-progressing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 06:04:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
